REFERENCE           02KYK001
NOTES               "in a by the book tone"
LANG_ENGLISH        "Ahem. This is one of the many training grounds here at the Academy. I'm going to put you two in separate courses. When you're ready, Jaden, go through that door."
LANG_CHINESE        "咳咳。这里是学院里的训练场地之一。我准备让你们分开训练。你准备好后就进那个门"

REFERENCE           02KYK002
NOTES               "to Rosh"
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rosh, follow me."
LANG_CHINESE        "洛西，你跟我来"

REFERENCE           02KYK003
LANG_ENGLISH        "This course will familiarize you with your core Force abilities. These are powers that every Force user has. As you progress in your training, you will learn new abilities. Both the light and dark sides will be open to you. Remember, abilities are not inherently good or evil. It's how you use them. Every Jedi is naturally stronger in different areas of the Force, and it will be up to you to decide what to focus on."
LANG_CHINESE        "今天的课程会带你们熟悉核心原力技能，这些是每个原力使用者都会的东西。\n随着你们训练不断深化，你们会学到新的技能。光明和黑暗原力都会向你们开放。\n记住，技能本身并无正邪之分，只是看你怎么用罢了。\n每个绝地武士天生擅长的原力领域各不相同，主修什么得你们自己决定"

REFERENCE           02KYK004
LANG_ENGLISH        "Alright, let's get started.  In the next area, you'll find some training remotes. These will help you learn how to handle a lightsaber. Ready?"
LANG_CHINESE        "行，我们开始吧。在下个场地，你们会遇到一些训练用遥控机器人。\n主要帮你们训练光剑的运用。准备好了吗"

