LANG_ENGLISH        "Done!"
LANG_CHINESE        "搞定了"

REFERENCE           02KYK006
NOTES               "looking over the wall"
LANG_ENGLISH        "Nice work, Rosh."
LANG_CHINESE        "不错啊，洛西"

REFERENCE           02KYK007
NOTES               "(to Jaden)"
LANG_ENGLISH        "You did well too, Jaden."
LANG_CHINESE        "你也不差，杰登"

REFERENCE           02KYK008
NOTES               "(to both of them)"
LANG_ENGLISH        "Your lightsaber is an invaluable tool. Even when inactive, it can defuse a potentially volatile situation. Trust me on that. As you train, you'll learn additional fighting styles. Changing styles during combat can surprise your opponent, allowing you to gain the upper hand."
LANG_CHINESE        "你们手里的光剑实在太有用了。就算挂在腰间，有时候也能稳定存在潜在危险的局势。\n不骗你们。随着训练的深入，你们会学到更多光剑的剑式。在战斗中多种剑式混用能让你占据上风，杀对手个措手不及"

REFERENCE           02KYK009
LANG_ENGLISH        "From here on out, we'll talk via comlink in each area. Let's move on."
LANG_CHINESE        "从这里开始，我们用对讲机联络。走吧"

REFERENCE           02KYK010
NOTES               "(via comm)"
LANG_ENGLISH        "Okay, Jaden.  You need to use the Force to jump across the ravine.  It shouldn't be a problem.  If you fall, jump back up to the bridge and try again."
LANG_CHINESE        "好，杰登，这里你得用原力跳过这个断桥。应该不成问题。如果你掉下去了，上桥再试一次"

REFERENCE           02KYK011
NOTES               "(via comm)"
LANG_ENGLISH        "You'll have to use Push to get out of here and into the next area."
LANG_CHINESE        "要到下个场地，你得“推"出一条路"

REFERENCE           02KYK012
NOTES               "(via comm)"
LANG_ENGLISH        "Remember: you can sense objects that can be affected by your powers.  Examine the area and see if anything stands out..."
LANG_CHINESE        "记住，你能感觉到那些能受你原力影响的物体。仔细查看这个地方，看看有没什么特别的东西"

REFERENCE           02ROP003
NOTES               "(laughing)"
LANG_ENGLISH        "Hey Jaden!  This should keep you busy 'til I finish the course!"
LANG_CHINESE        "嘿，杰登，等你搞定了这家伙时我应该已经完成训练了吧"

